Robots and UFOs

Key bindings:

General
  a          Toggle axes
  m          Change current mode
  ESC        Exit
  l          Toggles lighting
  c          Toggles GL_COLOR_MATERIAL

Orthogonal Mode
  arrows     Change view angle

Perspective Mode
  arrows     Change view angle
  +/-        Changes field of view

First Person Mode
  up/down      Move forwards/backwards
  left/right   Turn left/right
  PgUp/PgDn    Look up/down (less than 90 degrees)
  +/-          Changes field of view


Time spent: 9 hours